Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Fred Astaire, 1987
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xv03
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Jun 1987
Small in stature, a giant on the screen - an appreciation of the life and work of Fred Astaire. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less